body_html:
If you installed tensorflow through conda install those are packages not built/maintained by us.
Therefore, we wont be able to provide support on those packages.
Please reach out to Anaconda for support with those packages.

body:
If you installed tensorflow through `conda install` those are packages not built/maintained by us.
Therefore, we wont be able to provide support on those packages.
Please reach out to Anaconda for support with those packages.
